Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.57,0:00:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.23,0:00:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.06,0:00:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.40,0:00:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.57,0:00:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you just have to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.73,0:00:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words\Nlured men to the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.44,0:00:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in pursuit of dreams greater\Nthan they've ever dared
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to imagine! This is the time\Nknown as the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.85,0:00:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:00:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.19,0:00:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.53,0:01:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.90,0:01:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:02:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never be anything more\Nthan the son of a filthy pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A filthy pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.07,0:02:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I sympathize with you.\NI really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You must hate your\Ngreat idiot of a father
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,for abandoning his\Nfamily and his village,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,all because of his\Nmindless lust for treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare insult\Nmy father ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a normal guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You must hypnotize\Nthe rich girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then and only then will\NI have undisputed control
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of her enormous fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You better stay away\Nfrom that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP yelping]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look, we gotta run.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, be careful!\NYou're gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll all sound like lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N"Expose the plot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirate Butler, Captain Kuro!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT] Our captain's been\Ngone for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Luffy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably just\Nneeds some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever he gets\Nreally upset like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you can count on him\Nhanging out by the shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL]\NCaptain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Luffy was\Nsupposed to be with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL]\NCaptain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL yelp]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Luffy?\NIs he still at the shore?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, he looked really upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But why? Still mad\Nat the butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWho knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No! That wasn't just a mad face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That look was different!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the tragic face\Nof sheer desperation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.57,0:05:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you guys show us the\Nway to get down to that shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT] This smells\Nlike an adventure to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Something\Nhappened at the shore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION] I think this calls\Nfor the Usopp Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already! How do\Nwe get to this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NTerrible news.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates! Pirates are coming!\NEverybody run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't stand a chance!\NEverybody run! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] Tomorrow morning they're\Ngonna attack the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,we gotta get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:06:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone even listening\Nto me?! Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[VILLAGERS murmuring]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[VILLAGER D]\NAll right, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.82,0:06:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[VILLAGER E]\NWe can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're putting a stop\Nto this here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NNo! It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth this\Ntime! I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! We all know that\Nyou're nothing but a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It would do you some good
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to follow Klahadore's example\Nof hard work and honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] Everything he could\Nsay would sound like lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NOh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exactly what\NKlahadore's counting on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He ignored me because he\Nknew no one would believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY]\NAre these to your liking, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:07:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY] Custom made to\Nyour exact specifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was quite a trip to get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NThey're just perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for traveling\Nso far to get them for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a gift aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As of tomorrow, it will be\Nexactly three years to the day
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,since Klahadore arrived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always taken\Nsuch good care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[MERRY] He'll be delighted\Nto receive such a lovely gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NI hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hear me out everyone!\NOur lives depend on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates are gonna attack\Nthe village in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If we believed every\Nstory you ever told us,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we would've run\Nscreaming from the village
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,hundreds a times already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] Please, believe me!\NWe don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying\Nthis time. I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?!\NThey'll murder you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[VILLAGER E] You'll be lucky\Nif we don't murder you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NI'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[VILLAGER E] Get him!\NDon't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT]\NThis is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER]\NOur captain always comes here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to be alone and think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION]\NIt is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that\Nstraw hat guy is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NThe rocks sure are loose here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NLook! Down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,--Whoa!\N--Hey! It's that straw hat guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And his butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] Luffy, what did you do?!\NHow did this happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT]\NHe fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION]\NHe's a goner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.74,0:08:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER] So that's why our\Ncaptain looked so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY snoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha. Lazy bum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[yawning]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.40,0:09:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.15,0:09:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good. I was worried\Nyou wouldn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick! Run, Kaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's going to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's tricked the entire village!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Klahadore's really a\Ndeadly pirate captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a story?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NUh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't one of my stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth! I heard\Nit with my own ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NKlahadore is a pirate captain
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,who weaseled his way\Ninto your family's home
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,so he could steal your fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's pretended to be\Nyour butler for three years
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,so he can kill you\Nand inherit your money!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA] What are you\Ntalking about, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,His crew is gonna raid\Nthe village at dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.10,0:10:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the process,\Nyou're gonna get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Klahadore is a very bad man,\Nyour life is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:11:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NHe did treat you harshly earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and I understand that you're\Nhurt, but lying like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya, please.\NI'm telling you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NI'm telling you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS]\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates are going to\Nattack the village?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they're gonna kill Kaya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. That's what they said.\NNo question 'bout it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL yelping]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what made you think\Nit'd be a good time for a nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember going to sleep\Nor getting down here at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This proves it!\NKlahadore is a bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp saw right though him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he's on his way\Nto warn the villagers
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so they'll have\Ntime to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Those stupid pirates\Nwon't hurt anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,because the town\Nwill be abandoned
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,by the time they get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better run away\Ntoo if we wanna live!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER] All right, let's\Npack our treasure and--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS]\NRun like the wind! Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to stock up before\Nthe meat shop guy leaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] C'mon, that's not\Nreally the issue at hand here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NHello, Usopp. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What adventure are you\Ngoing to tell me about today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHmm. Well, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NOh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the story of\Nme fighting a giant gold fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,At the south pole, when\NI was only five years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA] A goldfish?\NYou fought a goldfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] A giant goldfish!\NIt was so huge,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,a fish tank the size\Nof this mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't be able to hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NOh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NWhat first astounded me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,was the immense\Nsize of its poop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.64,0:13:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was solid ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so big, that\Nwhen I landed on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was\Nsome kind of island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NUhh... That sounds fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.31,0:13:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] Believe me,\NI know it sounds fake,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but every word of it is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA, USOPP laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] My first mistake\Nwas lighting the bonfire
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:13:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to dry my clothes off with.\NThat was just plain dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NWhy's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NWell, the next thing I knew,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a giant gold fish\Nwith his rear end on fire
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,--and guess who he was mad at!\N--[KAYA] Oh, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NWell, I can't say I blame him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.02,0:14:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as he knew,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I trying to turn him into\Na giant grilled gold fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Every... one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All those lies you told me.\NThey brought joy to my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But... this is just\Nvengeful poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, I'm not just\Ntrying to get back at Klahadore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you do\Nthat? It's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP, KAYA laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Kaya, is everything\Nokay up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.27,0:14:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:14:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here!\NRight now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Unhand her immediately,\Nyou villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NPlease, trust me, Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta get out\Nof this village
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,before that butler gets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NC'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise this'll all\Nmake sense tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.57,0:15:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but right now we need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,--Please... Trust me.\N--[KAYA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[slap]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.11,0:16:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave Miss Kaya\Nalone, you maniac!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[VILLAGERS yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let that lunatic get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He broke in and tried to\Nkidnap the lady of the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[VILLAGERS yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't anyone believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:17:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[VILLAGERS yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there, ma'am,\Neverything's going to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO] After three\Nlong years of absence,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I made the call for\Nmy men, and you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Your loyalty will be\Nrichly rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I intend on being more than\Ngenerous when I divide the take.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,At dawn tomorrow, destroy the\Nvillage to your hearts content.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yelling, cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.57,0:17:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[KURO chuckling]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NWho're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:18:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] I'm Usopp,\Nbrave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard you've been\Na little down lately
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought I'd tell you\Na story to cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA] You would do well\Nto mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave or I'll call\Nsomeone who will make you leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NHey, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, I should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I've always been\Nmeddlesome like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha. It's not always\Na bad thing though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One time, when I\Nwas three years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,my meddling led me\Nto saving a sick whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA]\NWhat? A whale?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP]\NYou bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A whale of a whale even, and\Nit had a really sore throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I walked into his\Nmouth to check it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.57,0:18:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but he thought I was food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[KAYA laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS]\NCaptain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! How's it going guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,--[CARROT] Hey, captain!\N--[PEPPER] Look he's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[squeaks]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! You're alive again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:18:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.69,0:19:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! And I had\Na pretty good nap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.73,0:19:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He was sleeping the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.36,0:19:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, we heard all\Nabout those pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and their evil plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better hurry and warn\Nthe people in the village
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so they have time to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Warn the people...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We all know you're\Nnothing but a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It would do you some good
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to follow Klahadore's example\Nof hard work and honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, obviously,\NI'm lying like usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That butler made me\Nso mad with what he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd get him back and\Nsay that he was a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[KIDS, USOPP laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION]\NOh, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:20:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You put the straw hat\Nguy up to it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[ALL laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Where ya goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT] Honestly, you've\Nreally disappointed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though that\Nbutler guy is a jerk,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.49,0:20:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were better\Nthan lying to hurt someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and I admired you for being\Nsuch a kind-hearted person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION]\NAnd to think,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,we respected you\Nthis entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT]\NI was wrong about him, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER]\NSo was I.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.73,0:20:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARROT]\NLet's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[PEPPER]\NYeah, it's suppertime anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[ONION]\NWonder what we're having.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP yelping]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There. All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how come you lied to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:20:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because all I do is lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[USOPP] There's no way\Nanybody was gonna believe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,what I had to say.\NWhy should they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.65,0:21:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Because what you were telling\Nthem was the honest truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They are coming. And they're\Ngonna level this whole town.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but what am\NI supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll think I'm lying\Nif I try to warn them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone in the village thinks
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that tomorrow's just gonna\Nbe another normal day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They think I'm lying and\Nthat's all they need to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna stop those pirates\Nat the beach tomorrow myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all my fault\Nfor being such a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,if they drive me away with\Nbrooms or shoot me in the arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my village.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my home... and\NI love everyone in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:21:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a hell of a good guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,sending your cronies away\Nand going into battle alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.61,0:22:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NJust so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.53,0:22:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I have dibs on all the\Npirate treasure, you got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.02,0:22:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you want a little\Nhelp or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.40,0:22:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna help me fight\Nall these pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you said there's a whole\Nbuncha bad guys, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.31,0:22:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And you look scared\Nout of your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.36,0:22:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. For your information,\NI have nerves of steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm perfectly okay\Nwith tons of bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.24,0:22:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you're looking at\Nthe legendary Captain Usopp,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.10,0:22:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,brave warrior of the high seas!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.02,0:22:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Damnit! All right,\Nfine, I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.86,0:22:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why shouldn't I be?!\NThey're Captain Kuro's men!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.06,0:22:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys mean business!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.69,0:22:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.06,0:22:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you guys are sticking\Naround cause you pity me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.48,0:22:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,just leave! I don't need\Nyou laughin' at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.94,0:22:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not laughing at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're helping because\Nyou are honorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.31,0:22:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think we'd\Nrisk our lives out of pity?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:23:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw... You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.36,0:23:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.74,0:23:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.35,0:23:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.11,0:23:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.24,0:23:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.94,0:23:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.44,0:23:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.15,0:23:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.06,0:23:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.69,0:23:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.98,0:23:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.82,0:24:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.86,0:24:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.81,0:24:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.07,0:24:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.94,0:24:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.35,0:24:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Huh. Why did Usopp\Ncover this slope in oil?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.15,0:24:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NIt's part of his plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.69,0:24:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI]\NThat's a weird plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.15,0:24:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NSo, where are these pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.82,0:24:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] What?! They're\Nat the north shore!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.85,0:24:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NI'll go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.98,0:24:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[NAMI] They better not lay\Na finger on my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.15,0:24:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] North! North!\NWhich way is north?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.36,0:24:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NI'll get you for this, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.23,0:24:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOn the next One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.94,0:24:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"Clash with the\NBlack Cat Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.02,0:24:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Battle on the Slope!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.86,0:24:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

